metadata.description:
For this track, I wanted to pair a tech house beat with uplifting gospel vocals and a dash of organ to bring out the spiritual flavor. I sought to merge this energy with the uplifting message of gospel music, creating a unique and spiritually enriching dance-floor experience. 

Produced, Mixed & Mastered by Sam Smyers
